{"tid":2096541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中原及無綫申保就業計劃　涉款分別逾億及8500萬元","createTime":"2020-07-06T07:40:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T07:44:48.000Z","uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bceec51be2ffd1ec531c37e05311340bb5b7c2ca","tid":2096541,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:40:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>當你仲好興奮緊嗰一萬蚊<br />\n施永青：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「保就業」計劃公布第三批僱主名單，涉及約3萬名僱主及逾33萬名受薪僱員，工資補貼額合共約77億元。<strong>有過百間獲批資助公司的承諾受薪僱員人數為0</strong>，部分公司申領金額超過10萬元，包括「聯向企業有限公司」、「時信專業服務有限公司」及「本草唯物」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>至於申領最高金額的是「中原地產代理有限公司 」</strong>，涉及1億1500多萬元，承諾受薪僱員總數為5600多人；電視廣播有限公司申領8500多萬元，涉及3100多名僱員；美聯商業管理有限公司申領6300多萬元，涉及3100多名員工。零售業方面，周大福珠寶金行有限公司申領 7700多萬元，涉及2800多名員工；莎莎化妝品有限公司申領5900多萬元，承諾受薪僱員數目為2100多人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536059-20200706.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536059-20200706.htm&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FsemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=245e78f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536059-20200706.htm&h=420f4e43\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536059-20200706.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c09c336fa9ad308eaabf1b5039d17100833b3e93","tid":2096541,"uid":7542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:40:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0ggBftnYDQ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0ggBftnYDQ4&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FsemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=08730999\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0ggBftnYDQ4</a>"},{"pid":"826542f85f7e534592728a912984448aa89202d5","tid":2096541,"uid":326700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:41:51.000Z","msg":"TVB: 我唔炒人但係一年俾得萬五蚊人工"},{"pid":"a35f66a413c7a37384aadfc3adf32ab7896ce55b","tid":2096541,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"826542f85f7e534592728a912984448aa89202d5","tid":2096541,"uid":326700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:41:51.000Z","msg":"TVB: 我唔炒人但係一年俾得萬五蚊人工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:44:48.000Z","msg":"而家請啲幕後工作人員一個月都畀唔夠一萬<br />\n根本無人騷佢"}]}